OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet key rival Wes
OL,4,CStreeting amid open revolt in Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister will meet Health
OL,8,FSecretary Wes Streeting, one of his
OL,9,Fkey rivals for the Labour leadership,
OL,10,Fafter a tumultuous few days in which
OL,11,Ffour ministers resigned and at least
OL,12,F80 MPs called for him to quit.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer managed to cling on
OL,15,Fto power in Number 10 and see off an
OL,16,Fimmediate threat to his leadership,
OL,17,Fwith reports suggesting the front
OL,18,Frunners to succeed him lack the
OL,19,Fnumbers to launch a challenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
