PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778652345
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet key rival Wes
OL,4,CStreeting amid open revolt in Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FGreater Manchester mayor Andy Burnham,
OL,8,Fa leading figure from the soft-left of
OL,9,Fthe party, has not unveiled a path
OL,10,Fback into Parliament. He needs an MP
OL,11,Fwilling to stand aside so he could
OL,12,Ffight a by-election.
OL,14,FSources close to Energy Secretary Ed
OL,15,FMiliband, another potential soft-left
OL,16,Fchallenger, have denied reports that
OL,17,Fhe is preparing to run if Mr Streeting
OL,18,Ftriggers a contest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
