OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778652345
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet key rival Wes
OL,4,CStreeting amid open revolt in Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FSir Keir told his Cabinet the country
OL,8,F"expects us to get on with governing"
OL,9,Fand "that is what I am doing", but
OL,10,Favoided being directly challenged as
OL,11,Fhe declined to discuss his leadership
OL,12,Fduring the gathering or meet critics
OL,13,Findividually afterwards, the Press
OL,14,FAssociation understands.
OL,16,FHe said he would only speak to
OL,17,Fministers one-to-one about his fate,
OL,18,Fbut did not do so once Cabinet
OL,19,Fconcluded, according to sources.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@eO]qD@EOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
