OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778652345
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet key rival Wes
OL,4,CStreeting amid open revolt in Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FWhile Mr Streeting is not expected to
OL,8,Fsay anything after Wednesday's meeting
OL,9,Fthat could distract from the King's
OL,10,FSpeech, Politico reported that
OL,11,FBuckingham Palace had privately told
OL,12,FNumber 10 they do not want the King to
OL,13,Fbe dragged into the conversation.
OL,15,FThe importance of protecting Charles
OL,16,Ffrom the impression that he is being
OL,17,Fused for political ends was stressed
OL,18,Fto Sir Keir's officials, a person
OL,19,Ffamiliar with the matter told the
OL,20,Fpolitical news outlet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
