OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet key rival Wes
OL,4,CStreeting amid open revolt in Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FIt is understood there has been no
OL,8,Fsuggestion that the opening of
OL,9,FParliament would not go ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
